All Classes

  • All Classes Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    Command
    This class creates objects that encapsulate user actions that can cause the state of a issue to update.
    Command.CommandValue
    An enumeration that represents one of the five possible commands that a user can make for the Issue Manager.
    Command.Resolution
    An enumeration that represents the four possible ways a user can resolve an issue.
    Issue
    Concrete class representing the State Pattern context.
    Issue.IssueType
    An enumeration that represents the the type of issue.
    IssueList
    Concrete class that maintains a current list of Issues in the Issue Manager system.
    IssueManager
    IssueManager implements the Singleton design pattern and controls the creation and modification of IssueLists This class works with the files that contain the saved Issue.
    IssueManagerGUI
    Container for the IssueManager that has the menu options for new issue files, loading existing files, saving files and quitting.
    IssueReader
    This class has one public method readIssuesFromFile that receives a String with the file name to read from.
    IssueWriter
    IssueWriter has one public method writeIssuesToFile that receives a String with the file name to write to and a List of Issues to write.
